race.description: Regional Championship Heat: The Road To Ascot
race.comment: LEONARDO DA GREY (10) won comfortably over 1110m here two back before getting well back last start and rattling home to go under in a photo finish. The splits he ran there were very strong and with a better draw today, he's expected to sit much closer. Can go one better this time around. LUCKEE FLORAN (5) just missed two back before a 3.8/L defeat here most recently. Can mix his form a touch, but he maps to get every chance today for Staples who has had plenty of success when steering. Can bounce back. BOLTA (4) held on to beat LEONARDO DA GREY last start when they made their runs together down the outside. Will probably be giving him a head start today from the draw, but that looks a key form reference for this. SAFE HUSTLE (9) can work to the front and give a bold sight. THE RUSH (6) can return on a positive note.
